# Research OS v4
### Self-Evolving Research Operating System
> **Version:** v4.0
> **Purpose:** A universal research operating system for discovering, evaluating, validating, and evolving research contributions in any scientific discipline.

---

# Philosophy

Research is **not** a linear process.

It is an iterative process of continuously improving one's understanding of the world.

The objective of Research OS is therefore **not to generate papers**, but to continuously evolve a **World Model** that becomes increasingly capable of identifying meaningful research opportunities.

Every paper, experiment, discussion, reviewer comment, or failure updates this World Model.

