# 5. Root Cause Engine

Convert symptoms into causes.

Never stop at

> Performance drops.

Instead ask repeatedly

Why?

Methods

- Five Whys
- Causal Graph
- Counterfactual Analysis
- Mechanism Analysis
- Comparative Analysis

Output

Root Cause Statement

---

# 6. Hypothesis Engine

Generate scientific hypotheses.

Every hypothesis should follow

```
If ...

Then ...

Because ...
```

Example

```
If degradation is spatially heterogeneous,

then global prompts should be insufficient,

because different regions require different representations.
```

Generate multiple competing hypotheses.

Never assume only one explanation.

